ouncement of the cancellation of Anthrocon 2020 to email us at <a href="mailto:refunds@anthrocon.org">refunds@anthrocon.org</a>&nbsp; and select the method of cancellation.&nbsp; <strong>If no email is received within the 2 weeks the membership will automatically be deferred until 2021 and can no longer be refunded.&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp;If the convention is canceled it will be announced on our webpage at <a href="http://www.anthrocon.org">www.anthrocon.org</a> and on all of our active social media platforms.</p><p class="">To view the entire refund policy, visit <a href="https://www.anthrocon.org/refundpolicy">anthrocon.org/refundpolicy</a></p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Anthrocon Charity Bucket Brigade Sign-Ups Now Open!</title><dc:creator>Guest User</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2020 16:52:49 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.anthrocon.org/news/2020/3/16/anthrocon-charity-bucket-brigade-sign-ups-now-open</link><guid isPermaLink="false">59d2e7962994ca6597e2795c:59d2f8971f318d87163c5ecb:5e6fae377ba56776cffa8b74</guid><description><![CDATA[Fursuiters who would like to participate directly in the fundraising for 
